    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "qkkyz",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 3520,
      "name": "note1",
      "width": 390,
      "height": 120,
      "content": "INTERACTION RULES\n\n1. Only one overlay can be open at a time\n2. Clicking Menu icon must close the Actions panel (if open) before opening the Menu sheet\n3. Clicking the + button must close the Menu sheet (if open) before showing the Action options\n4. Clicking the X button or overlay closes the Actions panel\n5. Clicking Menu icon again or overlay closes the Menu sheet"
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "rUOzW",
      "x": 490,
      "y": 3520,
      "name": "note2",
      "width": 390,
      "height": 80,
      "content": "ACTIONS PANEL (Screen 2)\n\n- Circular action menu (like react-native-circular-action-menu)\n- 3 circle icon buttons fan out from the + button\n- Positioned on an arc: Income top, Expense bottom-left, Transfer bottom-right\n- Small labels below each circle\n- Animate: scale from 0 + translate from center\n- Center button rotates 45deg to become X\n- Dark overlay behind, tap to dismiss"
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "ukl0e",
      "x": 980,
      "y": 3520,
      "name": "note3",
      "width": 390,
      "height": 80,
      "content": "MENU SHEET (Screen 3)\n\n- Slides up from bottom nav top edge\n- Menu icon highlighted as active\n- Bottom nav remains visible and functional\n- Tap Menu icon again or overlay to close"
    },
